The Global Chess League is a 6-team double round-robin tournament taking place from June 22 to July 1, 2023 in Dubai, UAE.

Players receive 15 minutes for the entire game, plus a 10-second increment starting from move one. Wins with Black are worth 4 board points, wins with White 3, a draw 1. Official website: globalchessleague.com
